Package util

Class List<E>

java.lang.Object
util.List<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements in the list
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<E>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ListMethods
public class List<E> extends Object implements Iterable<E>
This class represents a list of appointments. It provides methods to add, remove, and manipulate the list, such as sorting and printing appointments by patient, location, or appointment details.
Author:
Raashi Maheshwari, Tanvi Yamarty
